What you need to know:

What started as a hobby is now a rewarding full-time enterprise for Salome Nyambura, an accountant.Nyambura, a mother of one, sought her husband's support to buy her first two female German Shepherd puppies worth Sh40,000 each for breeding.She later imported a Caucasian Ovcharka puppy from Romania.The mature German Shepherd gives birth twice a year, while the Caucasian Ovcharka gives birth once.